"{\"uid\": \"newzimbabwe.com-zimbabwe-olympics-committee-hopes-to-send-more-athletes-to-paris-2024-olympics\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Date: By Sports Reporter With less than six months before the 2024 Paris Olympics kicks off in France, the Zimbabwe Olympics Committee (Zimbabwe Olympics Committee) is still hopeful that more athletes can qualify to add to the obtaining numbers.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 247, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 97, \"end\": 103, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.7182779043639671, \"rank\": 0.36806011193021726, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 109, \"end\": 117, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zimbabwe\", \"score\": 0.9999999974611455, \"rank\": 2.5389203350353228e-09, \"text\": \"Zimbabwe\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zimbabwe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zimbabwe\"}, {\"begin\": 138, \"end\": 146, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zimbabwe\", \"score\": 0.9999999974611455, \"rank\": 2.5389203350353228e-09, \"text\": \"Zimbabwe\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zimbabwe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zimbabwe\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sports Reporter\", \"from\": 9, \"to\": 24}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 58, \"to\": 81}, {\"ngram\": \"more athletes\", \"from\": 187, \"to\": 200}, {\"ngram\": \"the obtaining numbers\", \"from\": 223, \"to\": 244}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the present moment, only two athletes have qualified for Paris 2024, long-distance runner Issac Mpofu and rower Stephen Cox.\", \"from\": 249, \"to\": 376, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 309, \"end\": 319, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999979536, \"rank\": 1.983422313998694e-12, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 364, \"end\": 375, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephen_D._Cox\", \"score\": 0.9999999993931397, \"rank\": 3.2602770821289934e-10, \"text\": \"Stephen Cox\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephen_D._Cox\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephen_D._Cox\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the present moment\", \"from\": 252, \"to\": 270}, {\"ngram\": \"only two athletes\", \"from\": 272, \"to\": 289}, {\"ngram\": \"long-distance runner Issac Mpofu\", \"from\": 321, \"to\": 353}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Zimbabwe had five athletes during the 2020 Tokyo Olympics, the lowest ever representatives as compared to all the previous editions.\", \"from\": 378, \"to\": 510, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 378, \"end\": 386, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zimbabwe\", \"score\": 0.9999999974611455, \"rank\": 2.5389203350353228e-09, \"text\": \"Zimbabwe\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zimbabwe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zimbabwe\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"five athletes\", \"from\": 391, \"to\": 404}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2020 Tokyo Olympics\", \"from\": 412, \"to\": 435}, {\"ngram\": \"the lowest ever representatives\", \"from\": 437, \"to\": 468}, {\"ngram\": \"all the previous editions\", \"from\": 484, \"to\": 509}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Initially, ZOC had set a target of sending ten individual athletes and one team sport but the dream seems to be in vain as all team sports have failed and hope is now on a few individual athletes in swimming and athletics.\", \"from\": 512, \"to\": 734, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 523, \"end\": 526, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ZOC_(band)\", \"score\": 0.5622702900110762, \"rank\": 0.5625000000000571, \"text\": \"ZOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ZOC_(band)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ZOC_(band)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a target\", \"from\": 535, \"to\": 543}, {\"ngram\": \"ten individual athletes\", \"from\": 555, \"to\": 578}, {\"ngram\": \"one team sport\", \"from\": 583, \"to\": 597}, {\"ngram\": \"the dream\", \"from\": 602, \"to\": 611}, {\"ngram\": \"all team sports\", \"from\": 635, \"to\": 650}, {\"ngram\": \"a few individual athletes\", \"from\": 682, \"to\": 707}, {\"ngram\": \"swimming\", \"from\": 711, \"to\": 719}, {\"ngram\": \"athletics\", \"from\": 724, \"to\": 733}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are still hoping for eight or more athletes to qualify, our target was ten and we remain optimistic that we will have more athletes qualifying.\", \"from\": 736, \"to\": 883, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"eight or more athletes\", \"from\": 761, \"to\": 783}, {\"ngram\": \"our target\", \"from\": 796, \"to\": 806}, {\"ngram\": \"more athletes\", \"from\": 858, \"to\": 871}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is still enough qualifying time in other sporting disciplines like athletics and swimming which will end in June.\", \"from\": 885, \"to\": 1005, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"enough qualifying time\", \"from\": 901, \"to\": 923}, {\"ngram\": \"other sporting disciplines\", \"from\": 927, \"to\": 953}, {\"ngram\": \"athletics\", \"from\": 959, \"to\": 968}, {\"ngram\": \"swimming\", \"from\": 973, \"to\": 981}, {\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 1000, \"to\": 1004}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So we are giving them enough support we can, through the solidarity funding but still it's not enough.\", \"from\": 1007, \"to\": 1110, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"enough support\", \"from\": 1030, \"to\": 1044}, {\"ngram\": \"the solidarity funding\", \"from\": 1061, \"to\": 1083}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are doing our best to work 